笑唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30011dd407c064b5758f8fd40f67ea322bd7cdf3","tid":1764468,"uid":53062,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T07:50:02.000Z","msg":"唔用腦真係害死人，燒自己後路"},{"pid":"d022261473d8d120786ae050a5129755644f5e0c","tid":1764468,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T07:54:53.000Z","msg":"犬未必敢追入路軌"},{"pid":"e7d07cb8cd0439f0fea0008d48ad4d413b9b3b8d","tid":1764468,"uid":77788,"like":4,"dislike":39,"score":-35,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T08:01:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6dcb0b6d96ac2965f077d8b8eb3d1e42e4f781fc","tid":1764468,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T08:02:33.000Z","msg":"狗特登燒？"},{"pid":"e1b4b27283f093bc29d6a30d580c0a73ff18b9f4","tid":1764468,"uid":201464,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"quote":{"pid":"e7d07cb8cd0439f0fea0008d48ad4d413b9b3b8d","tid":1764468,"uid":77788,"like":4,"dislike":39,"score":-35,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T08:01:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T08:03:49.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#77788 - 書面語達人(五毛)</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span>, 請大家多加注意, 善用不推文回覆！<br />\n該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>自從手足開始掘磚，坐輪椅嘅阿嫲就冇出過街⋯⋯ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>而家每日要500蚊請人去照顧阿嫲<br />\n2星期已經用咗我老豆一半人工<br />\n下個月可能畀唔起租，要瞓街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1743564/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1743564/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>我諗到一招可以幫理大手足殺出重圍！麻煩推上熱門！ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://media0.giphy.com/media/3o6YgbkGykmLBUgfM4/source.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia0.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F3o6YgbkGykmLBUgfM4%2Fsource.gif&h=6e68d952&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n向警方無條件投降<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1730097/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1730097/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>淺藍老豆：如果香港交畀中大班黑衣人管，世界真係大亂 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>我一時語塞，完全唔知點駁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次示威形象被中大佔領拖累晒<br />\n原來最勇最激嗰批前線真係冇腦嘅<br />\n衝動、蠻不講理、以武屈人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都開始猶豫仲應唔應該支持呢場運動</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1724886/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1724886/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>又一城真係死咗人呀！快啲過嚟 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>2015年7月31日 (五)<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n中年漢又一城墮斃<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】中年漢商場內跳樓，飛墮六層樓亡！現場九龍塘又一城商場，昨晚九時許，一名男子在商場內L2樓層，攀出玻璃圍欄，危坐圍欄外壆邊上，有保安員見狀報警，警員及消防員接報到場，在圍欄內向他游說，但大約廿分鐘後，事主卻突然縱身躍下，直墮六個樓層，跌落LG2樓層，當時該層地面正舉行「傻豹‧粉紅大派對」展覽，事主壓中展覽設置的平台，將平台壓爆，重傷倒臥，奄奄一息，由救護員送院救治，證實死亡，警方檢視死者遺下斜孭袋內的證件，相信死者姓周（四十一歲），相信事件無可疑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1704338/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1704338/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>美國怕香港搞臨時政府，係因為冇泛民黎智英黃之鋒等「信得過」嘅人撐場！！！ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>泛民、黎智英、黃之鋒同美國政府一向有交情，係美國信得過嘅民主派政客。當中，有人坐過政治監，有人放棄服裝生意。但係你哋班無名氏無端端搞臨時政府，美國根本唔知你係乜水，唔可能貿然支持你。最怕就係有中共滲透臨時政府，甚至係中共牽頭，美國撐錯人就戇鳩鳩喇。唔好忘記，3年前好多香港人都唔信梁天琦，覺得佢出嚟</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1631492/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1631492/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a>"},{"pid":"2f762a9b666d7510d83cff2dc4c61172687b0d92","tid":1764468,"uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T02:39:46.000Z","msg":"警世"},{"pid":"fe93492e31cd00500ac14728dd6fcf06499c027e","tid":1764468,"uid":69761,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T02:45:58.000Z","msg":"堅持攬抄<br />\n商家唔洗諗有返生意<br />\n簡單和你shop,和你唱 ,和你lunch已經好有用<br />\n唔好諗住聖誕,新年,復活有生意做<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"0edb2ee03f6f0c1232519ef0386f516790f52439","tid":1764468,"uid":166149,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e7d07cb8cd0439f0fea0008d48ad4d413b9b3b8d","tid":1764468,"uid":77788,"like":4,"dislike":39,"score":-35,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T08:01:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T02:47:21.000Z","msg":"同班鬼齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602fc093c780d48e265f5957fc9998c1066c2570","tid":1764468,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T02:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24df00ff7cb23e785c5187109c574f47a44e9187","tid":1764468,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T02:54:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6370712c2cd8774c186c14b625fc74acb1b580df","tid":1764468,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20